OL,4,Cput my life 'more at risk' from Taliban
OL,6,FAfter working in what he described as
OL,7,Fa "dangerous" role for the UK
OL,8,Fmilitary, he was left behind, like
OL,9,Fmany others, during Britain's chaotic
OL,10,Fevacuation from Kabul in August 2021.
OL,12,FTo support those left behind and at
OL,13,Fserious risk from the Taliban, the
OL,14,Fgovernment launched the Afghan
OL,15,FRelocations and Assistance Policy
OL,16,F(Arap), which offers relocation to the
OL,17,FUK for those who qualify.
