OL,3,CAfghan army officer: UK data breach
OL,4,Cput my life 'more at risk' from Taliban
OL,6,FBut in February 2022, a defence
OL,7,Fofficial accidentally released a
OL,8,Fdataset containing the personal
OL,9,Fdetails of nearly 19,000 Arap
OL,10,Fapplicants.
OL,12,FThe Ministry of Defence only became
OL,13,Faware of the breach in August 2023,
OL,14,Fwhen parts of the dataset were
OL,15,Fanonymously posted in a Facebook group.
OL,17,FA superinjunction was issued by the
OL,18,FHigh Court to try to stop the Taliban
OL,19,Ffrom discovering the leak.
