OL,3,CAfghan army officer: UK data breach
OL,4,Cput my life 'more at risk' from Taliban
OL,6,FThat injunction was lifted on Tuesday
OL,7,Fafter a review. Those affected were
OL,8,Fcontacted by email and warned of the
OL,9,Fpotential danger.
OL,11,FITV News has spoken to a man who fled
OL,12,FAfghanistan to protect himself and his
OL,13,Ffamily while on the run from the
OL,14,FTaliban.
OL,16,FFor security reasons, we cannot reveal
OL,17,Fhis exact role. He told us that
OL,18,Fdespite taking precautions since 2021,
OL,19,Fthe data leak has made his life even
OL,20,Fharder.
