OL,3,CAfghan army officer: UK data breach
OL,4,Cput my life 'more at risk' from Taliban
OL,6,F"The UK Government's data breach has
OL,7,Fmade things even harder. It exposed my
OL,8,Fpersonal information, making me and
OL,9,Fothers even more at risk," he said.
OL,11,FThough he added that even with "all
OL,12,Fhis suffering," he does not regret
OL,13,Fhelping the UK mission.
