OL,3,CAfghan army officer: UK data breach
OL,4,Cput my life 'more at risk' from Taliban
OL,6,FHe said that when the Taliban took
OL,7,Fover in 2021, they came to his home
OL,8,Fthree times looking for him.
OL,10,FFearing for his life, he said he had
OL,11,F"no choice" but to flee to another
OL,12,Fcountry.
OL,14,FNow on the run, he said: "I'm jobless.
OL,15,FI do heavy jobs like truck loading and
OL,16,Fother things, just to buy food and pay
OL,17,Frent."
OL,19,FHe hopes, like others, that he will
OL,20,Freceive an offer to relocate to the UK
OL,21,Funder the Arap.
